Package: historytracers
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Teaching is often a daily challenge for both students and teachers,
 each for different reasons.
 Our goal is to support both sides of the learning process by providing diverse tools.

Package: historytracers-images
Architecture: all
Depends: historytracers (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Images for History Tracers
 Provides the image files used by the History Tracers viewer,
 excluding the img_options.json configuration file.

Package: historytracers-devel
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for History Tracers
 Source code and development files for the History Tracers
 teaching tool.  Contains the complete repository source tree
 excluding the pre-built www/ directory.
